  "detailed_description": "The Great Pickle Adventure is at its heart a pickle-based platformer. <br><br>During early access expect to have many frequent updates shaped by the community. Updates can range from mechanics changes to level updates to completely new levels and features. <br><br>Explore 20+ themed levels and special play levels<br><br>Move as fast as you can to get the best time possible or explore at your leisure<br><br>Fight through 20+ enemies to gain XP and buy upgrades in the shop<br><br>Tired of the constant timer? Try out the built-in RPG or 9 levels of breakout in Special Levels.<br><br>Join our discord: ",
